Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿她...埃拉诺…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧得更厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿冰来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈、普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳们说...刚才我梦到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妈妈、普莉西丝一起在外面玩得好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的天空又宽又大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有好多漂亮的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃拉诺、埃拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊!比我想得还要快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子恐怕…恐怕活不了太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能救救她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用的办法我都用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够找到月光花的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝…已经让村民分成几路去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不敢保证她不会进入林卡圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能够尽快找到月光花回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼医生，您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃拉诺这边就要请波曼医师多费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个只不过是一个古代生物的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一只小免子，喂…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免子怎么变成了怪物了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以被牠打败呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把月光花找到带回村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我制造的东西还是第一次成功的达成任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿，你怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我好像听到普莉西丝的声音哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我什么都没有听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再拖拖拉拉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从现在开始得要用走的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛~~~ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要突然这么大声行不行啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我担心嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，你有没有听到什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…依我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝也许还没有到这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，是你听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…是有这个垫着的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爬上去很困难欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有试试这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过了这片森林之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是林卡圣地的中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方应该有长月光花才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳们不觉得很奇怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林卡圣地应该是个充满危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们到现在都还没有遇到任何的怪物欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听…有声音欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了，艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这一次非常确定是个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的听到普莉西丝的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘!没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是有什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁可以…救救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我，救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝，我马上去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿，危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请掌管『火』之火界王巴拉蒙赐予我祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请汝带着宛如火箭之身来此降威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火焚墙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个…陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个冒牌货应该可以露出真面目了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没意思欸，怎么会被妳识破了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳是普莉西丝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就应该会直接向克劳德求救才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是找艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的普莉西丝在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳少装蒜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道她到过这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有多久就被小免子给追跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小免子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，牠是我的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多免子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个体型好像差太多了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠们都是我最宝贝的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠们一直在这里等你们来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪我们在路上都没有碰到什么妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个人呢，马上就会变成我的养分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小免子们通通一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天雷电波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭怪物，竟敢用普莉西丝的样子骗我!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个怎么会这么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这关系到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个叫做埃拉诺的小女孩的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都要去哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就只剩下妳一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳还想继续打吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…我以后不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你们道歉，不要打我 我们没有要打妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一次主要是要找一种叫做月光花的草药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一找到我们就会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过妳得答应我们今后不再攻击人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不攻击人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她真的不攻击人类的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不是非杀她不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我们真的可以相信她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道月光花开在什么地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜、塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳说的那些全是胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟，是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光花真的就在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是才说不攻击人类的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，说得也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我立刻放了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，在这之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾…蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让电光明灭的雷界王米塔龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让世人见识你的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天雷电波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是被我亲过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全都会变成供我使唤的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是答应过你们，我自己是不会去攻击人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她们就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和埃拉诺比起来，这根本就不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等着，埃拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就带月光花回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有找到月光花吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳还好吧?埃拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她顶多只能再撑个半天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到处都找过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝好像不在林卡镇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她真的是去林卡圣地了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望她不要出事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在能做的也只有祈祷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们能够尽快的带着月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安的回到村子里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快点醒醒啊，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你孕育光芒一闪的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些恶徒卑鄙的心思一次迎头痛击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波神箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个也不要老是躲来躲去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她们打一打嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得我都觉得没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过要保护蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会伤害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，那你就等着被她打死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的应该是塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离得再远她也会攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想办法阻挡她的攻击才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，我需要你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时帮我阻挡蕾娜的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么挡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上格斗术的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学过一套阻挡对方攻击的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有试试看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，小圆我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育光芒一闪的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些恶徒卑鄙的心思一次迎头痛击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把妳打到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个就会正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再上妳的当了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没有办法…杀女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像白水晶一样闪耀的花朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到魔石的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让整个森林都变了样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在她清醒前融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿，这是你搞的鬼对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上给我解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了要打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我得去找月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖怪说得对，这里本来有月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它们的营养定全被怪物吸掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是......
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好不容易才到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是普莉西丝的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿你怎么又来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在马上拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…我好不容易才拿到月光花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还说好，等她好了要一起出去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事上都会说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子在这个时候及时赶到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妳…我一直在找妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?有没有哪里受伤?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子埃拉诺有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了妳，普莉西丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经渡过危险期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是等她的体力恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，波曼医生谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢你，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿，好可怜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就猜到会有这种结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳好了以后我们一起去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，普莉西丝

